F with a WebP fallback.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"font-semibold text-foreground\",\"children\":\"Why is AVIF greyed out in the format dropdown?\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1\",\"children\":\"AVIF encoding requires browser support. If the AVIF option is disabled, your browser cannot encode AVIF images. Chrome, Edge, and recent Firefox versions support AVIF encoding. Safari support is still limited.\"}]]}]]}]\n27:[[\"$\",\"meta\",\"0\",{\"charSet\":\"utf-8\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"1\",{\"name\":\"viewport\",\"content\":\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\"}]]\n39:I[27201,[\"/_next/static/chunks/0zif8_3mgcc0x.js\",\"/_next/static/chunks/0zv.me6xdrdsz.js\",\"/_next/static/chunks/0ag6f0zogt0qg.js\",\"/_next/static/chunks/04p0ygcx_g620.js\",\"/_next/static/chunks/0d3shmwh5_nmn.js\",\"/_next/static/chunks/0_pa1c_tsbiw0.js\",\"/_next/static/chunks/10nuyoal1pib2.js\"],\"IconMark\"]\n2a:[[\"$\",\"title\",\"0\",{\"children\":\"Free Image Converter Online — No Sign Up | Free Tool Shed\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"1\",{\"name\":\"description\",\"content\":\"Convert images between PNG, JPG, WebP, and AVIF with quality controls. Bulk convert, resize, and download — free, no sign-up, 100% browser-based. A free alternative to Adobe Photoshop. No sign up required.\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"2\",{\"name\":\"google-adsense-account\",\"content\":\"ca-pub-7700405385978151\"}],[\"$\",\"link\",\"3\",{\"rel\":\"canonical\",\"href\":\"https://freetoolshed.com/tools/media-toolkit/image-converter\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"4\",{\"property\":\"og:title\",\"content\":\"Free Image Converter Online — No Sign Up | Free Tool Shed\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"5\",{\"property\":\"og:description\",\"content\":\"Convert images between PNG, JPG, WebP, and AVIF with quality controls. Bulk convert, resize, and download — free, no sign-up, 100% browser-based. A free alternative to Adobe Photoshop. No sign up required.\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"6\",{\"property\":\"og:url\