size limits.\"]}]]}],[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-10 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight\",\"children\":\"How to Convert Images\"}],[\"$\",\"ol\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-4 space-y-2 text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"1. Add images\"}],\" — Drag and drop image files into the upload area, or click to browse. Add files in multiple batches if needed.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"2. Choose format\"}],\" — Select your target format: PNG, JPG, WebP, or AVIF.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"3. Set quality\"}],\" — For lossy formats, adjust the quality slider (1-100%). Higher values produce better quality but larger files. PNG is always lossless.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"4. Optional resize\"}],\" — Enter a max dimension in pixels to scale down large images. Leave blank to keep the original size.\"]}],[\"$\",\"li\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"strong\",null,{\"children\":\"5. Convert & download\"}],\" — Click Convert and download each file individually, or use Download All for the entire batch.\"]}]]}],[[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"aria-labelledby\":\"tool-insights-tips\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"id\":\"tool-insights-tips\",\"className\":\"text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight\",\"children\":[\"Tips from Building \",\"the Image Converter\"]}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-3 max-w-3xl text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Notes from designing and testing this tool — what we kept in mind, the edge cases we worked around, and the small choices that make the difference between a tool that ships and one that breaks on real input.\"}],[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-4 grid max-w-3xl gap-3\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",\"WebP and AVIF are smaller than JPEG at the same quality\",{\"className\":\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L10\",null,{\"iconNode\":[[\"path\",{\"d\":\"M15 14c.2-1 .7-1.7 1.5-2.5 1-.9 1.5-2.2 1.5-3.5A6 6 0 0 0 6 8c0 1 .2 2.2 1.5 3.5.7.7 1.3 1.5 1.5 2.5\",\"key\":\"1gvzjb\"}],[\"path\",{\"d\":\"M9 18h6\",\"key\":\"x1upvd\"}],[\"path\",{\"d\":\"M10 22h4\",\"key\":\"ceow96\"}]],\"className\":\"lucide-lightbulb mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-brand\"}],\"$L14\"]}],\"$L15\",\"$L16\",\"$L17\"]}]]}],\"$L18\",\"$L19\"],\"$L1a\",\"$L1b\",\"$L1c\",\"$L1d\"]}]\nd:[\"$\",\"script\",\"script-0\",{\"src\":\"/_next/static/chunks/0my44zep2qx-6.js\",\"async\":true}]\ne:[\"$\",\"$L1e\",null,{\"children\":[\"$\",\"$1f\",null,{\"name\":\"Next.MetadataOutlet\",\"children\":\"$@20\"}]}]\n14:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"WebP and AVIF are smaller than JPEG at the same quality\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"For web use, WebP is ~25–35% smaller than JPEG at visually identical quality; AVIF is ~50% smaller. Browser support is now universal — there's little reason to ship JPEG for new web work.\"}]]}]\n15:[\"$\",\"li\",\"PNG only for graphics with sharp edges or transparency\",{\"className\":\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L10\",null,{\"iconNode\":\"$c:props:children:8:0:props:children:2:props:children:0:props:children:0:props:iconNode\",\"className\":\"lucide-lightbulb mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-brand\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"PNG only for graphics with sharp edges or transparency\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"PNG is lossless but huge for photographs. Use it for screenshots, logos, and UI elements; use JPEG/WebP/AVIF for photos. Mixing them up is the most common reason images load slowly.\"}]]}]]}]\n16:[\"$\",\"li\",\"Resize before compressing for max savings\",{\"className\":\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L10\",null,{\"iconNode\":\"$c:props:children:8:0:props:children:2:props:children:0:props:children:0:props:iconNode\",\"className\":\"lucide-lightbulb mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-brand\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Resize before compressing for max savings\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"A 4000×3000 photo at quality 60 is bigger than a 1600×1200 photo at quality 85. Most web destinations don't need 4K source resolution — downsize first, compress second.\"}]]}]]}]\n17:[\"$\",\"li\",\"Batch with consistent settings, then spot-check\",{\"className\":\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L10\",null,{\"iconNode\":\"$c:props:children:8:0:props:children:2:props:children:0:props:children:0:props:iconNode\",\"className\":\"lucide-lightbulb mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-brand\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Batch with consistent settings, then spot-check\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"When converting many images, set one tuning (quality, max dimensions) for the whole batch. Then spot-check 2–3 representative outputs before publishing.\"}]]}]]}]\n18:[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"aria-labelledby\":\"tool-insights-mistakes\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"id\":\"tool-insights-mistakes\",\"className\":\"text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight\",\"children\":\"Common Mistakes to Avoid\"}],[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-4 grid max-w-3xl gap-3\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",\"Setting JPEG quality to 100\",{\"className\":\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L10\",null,{\"iconNode\":[[\"path\",{\"d\":\"m21.73 18-8-14a2 2 0 0 0-3.48 0l-8 14A2 2 0 0 0 4 21h16a2 2 0 0 0 1.73-3\",\"key\":\"wmoenq\"}],[\"path\",{\"d\":\"M12 9v4\",\"key\":\"juzpu7\"}],[\"path\",{\"d\":\"M12 17h.01\",\"key\":\"p32p05\"}]],\"className\":\"lucide-triangle-alert mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-pink-500\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Setting JPEG quality to 100\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Quality 100 is barely distinguishable from 92–95 to the eye but produces a much larger file. The sweet spot for web JPEG is usually 75–85.\"}]]}]]}],[\"$\",\"li\",\"Converting screenshots to JPEG\",{\"className\":\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L10\",null,{\"iconNode\":\"$18:props:children:1:props:children:0:props:children:0:props:iconNode\",\"className\":\"lucide-triangle-alert mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-pink-500\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Converting screenshots to JPEG\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"JPEG's compression smears sharp pixel boundaries — exactly what screenshots are made of. Use PNG or WebP for screenshots; JPEG makes them look fuzzy and adds compression artifacts around text.\"}]]}]]}],[\"$\",\"li\",\"Forgetting to strip EXIF metadata\",{\"className\":\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L10\",null,{\"iconNode\":\"$18:props:children:1:props:children:0:props:children:0:props:iconNode\",\"className\":\"lucide-triangle-alert mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-pink-500\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Forgetting to strip EXIF metadata\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Photos from phones embed GPS coordinates, device info, and timestamps in EXIF. Strip metadata before publishing photos online unless that data is intentional.\"}]]}]]}]]}]]}]\n19:[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"aria-labelledby\":\"tool-insights-takeaways\",\"className\":\"rounded-lg border border-brand/30 bg-brand/5 p-5\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"id\":\"tool-insights-takeaways\",\"className\":\"text-lg font-semibold tracking-tight\",\"children\":\"Key Takeaways\"}],[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-3 space-y-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",\"The Image Converter handles JPEG, PNG, WebP, AVIF, BMP, and TIFF with per-file quality and resize settings.\",{\"className\":\"flex items-start gap-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L10\",null,{\"iconNode\":[[\"circle\",{\"cx\":\"12\",\"cy\":\"12\",\"r\":\"10\",\"key\":\"1mglay\"}],[\"path\",{\"d\":\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\",\"key\":\"dzmm74\"}]],\"className\":\"lucide-circle-check mt-0.5 size-4 shrink-0 text-brand\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm text-foreground\",\"children\":\"The Image Converter handles JPEG, PNG, WebP, AVIF, BMP, and TIFF with per-file quality and resize settings.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"li\",\"Batch mode converts multiple files at once with a shared or per-file configuration.\",{\"className\":\"flex items-start gap-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L10\",null,{\"iconNode\":\"$19:props:children:1:props:children:0:props:children:0:props:iconNode\",\"className\":\"lucide-circle-check mt-0.5 size-4 shrink-0 text-brand\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm text-foreground\",\"children\":\"Batch mode converts multiple files at once with a shared or per-file configuration.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"li\",\"All processing runs locally; image data never uploads.\",{\"className\":\"flex items-start gap-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L10\",null,{\"iconNode\":\"$19:props:children:1:props:children:0:props:children:0:props:iconNode\",\"className\":\"lucide-circle-check mt-0.5 size-4 shrink-0 text-brand\"}],[\"